    "The method can generate lowdimensional, highly descriptive features and intercommunicate these features between different sensors and indoor and outdoor scenes.",
    "This undoubtedly enhances the generalization ability of the network.",
    "At the same time, the low dimensional feature descriptors generated by the method (only 16 or 32 output dimensions) greatly speed up the corresponding search, which makes the realtime application of the method possible.",
    "The local feature extraction method to ensure the input network's rotation invariance brings additional computing consumption.",
    "At the same time, it is sensitive to the initial pose of the source point cloud and noise anomalies."
